PROCESS

How Coaching Works

Our experts dispel myths about the futility of coaching and offer only real knowledge that you can apply in practice. Here's how we work:

Problem Identification

Each entrepreneur comes to us with a specific problem or request. Tell us about your needs.

Lectures

We offer intensive courses in a variety of business areas. Only real knowledge and case studies.

Personal Consultations

In one-on-one sessions with a coach, you can ask him or her any questions and get a clear plan of action.

Analysis of Results

Together with the coach, you analyze the results of the implemented changes and plan further actions.

ABOUT US

We Care About Your Success

If you are an entrepreneur, you have two paths to develop. You learn either from your own or from others' mistakes. Our experts help you take the second path.

━ Our Mission

We have brought together practicing entrepreneurs so that they can share their experience with other budding businessmen and give valuable advice to those who need it.

━ Our Vision

We believe that effective coaching is all about relevant skills, practice, and great results obtained when working closely with an experienced mentor that can give you valuable advice.

"We need to accept that we won’t always make the right decisions, that we’ll screw up royally sometimes – understanding that failures are not the opposite of success – it’s part of success."

Arianna Huffington – CEO of Thrive Global

FAQ

Have Any Questions?

We are happy to work with entrepreneurs of any scale. Our mission is to help you set your own business goals and move successfully towards them with open eyes.

  • Who are the coaches?

    Our coaches are experienced top managers, department heads, and founders of well-known companies.

  • Can I buy only one personal consultation?

    Yes, you can find the pricing plan below or just contact us to make an appointment with one of our coaches.

  • What do your courses consist of?

    We offer intensive min-courses in basic business, financial, marketing, and other disciplines. Each course includes theory, practice, and real case studies from our coaches.

  • What should I choose if I'm only starting my business?

    We suggest you signing up for our Strategy & Planning course and have 2-3 one-on-one sessions with our coach.

  • Are your courses online of offline?

    We have both options.

Business Strategy

Any business starts with planning. We will help you develop an effective strategy. 

Marketing

We cover all aspects of marketing, from paid ads to offline activities. 

Financial Processes

Budgeting, fundraising, accounting, and other issues are covered by our coaches. 

Data Analysis

We tell about big data and how to analyze it to run your business more efficiently.
